  "texts": [
    "GPT-Neo represents a pivotal step towards democratizing access to state-ofthe-art AI technologies, offering a platform for experimentation and innovation in the field.",
    "Despite its advancements, GPT-Neo, like its predecessors, faces the challenge of static knowledge-a limitation that this paper aims to address through the concept of incremental knowledge enrichment.",
    "Incremental knowledge enrichment seeks to devise a method by which GPT-Neo can seamlessly integrate new information into its existing knowledge base, without the need for comprehensive retraining.",
    "This approach proposes a paradigm shift from static to dynamic knowledge management, envisioning a future where LLMs can remain perpetually current, reflective of the latest developments and discoveries.The proposition of incremental knowledge enrichment for GPT-Neo introduces a series of technical and theoretical challenges, ranging from the selection and verification of real-time data sources to the integration of new information in a manner that preserves the model's coherence and reliability.",
    "This endeavor necessitates a multidisciplinary approach, drawing upon insights from machine learning, data management, and cybersecurity to ensure the integrity and efficacy of the enriched knowledge base."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}